e/1254624-night-always-comes/watch?locale=ZW","flatrate":[{"logo_path":"/pbpMk2JmcoNnQwx5JGpXngfoWtp.jpg","provider_id":8,"provider_name":"Netflix","display_priority":4}]}}},"wikidata_id":"Q126077186","tvdb_id":null,"wikipedia_url":"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Night_Always_Comes","overview_source":"tmdb","import_batch_id":null,"import_batch_name":null,"imported_at":"2026-02-21T22:12:46.088062+00:00","region":null,"main_poster":null,"images":null,"enriched_at":null,"enrichment_cycle":0,"translations":[{"data":{"title":"","runtime":108,"tagline":"$$25,000. 1 night. No other options.","homepage":"https://www.netflix.com/title/81770158","overview":"Facing eviction in a city her family can no longer afford, a woman plunges into a desperate and increasingly dangerous all-night search to raise $25,000."},"name":"English","iso_639_1":"en","iso_3166_1":"US","english_name":"English"},{"data":{"title":"","runtime":108,"tagline":"$$25.000. 1 nuit. Pas d'autres options.","homepage":"https://www.netflix.com/fr/title/81770158","overview":"Menacée d'expulsion dans une ville devenue trop chère pour sa famille, une femme s'enfonce au cœur d'une nuit sombre et périlleuse dans l'espoir de réunir 25 000 dollars."},"name":"Français","iso_639_1":"fr","iso_3166_1":"FR","english_name":"French"},{"data":{"title":"La notte arriva sempre","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"https://www.netflix.com/it/title/81770158","overview":"Di fronte allo sfratto in una città ormai troppo cara per la sua famiglia, una donna si lancia in una disperata e sempre più rischiosa ricerca notturna per trovare 25.000 dollari."},"name":"Italiano","iso_639_1":"it","iso_3166_1":"IT","english_name":"Italian"},{"data":{"title":"밤은 늘 찾아온다","runtime":108,"tagline":"","homepage":"https://www.netflix.com/kr/title/81770158","overview":"주거비 상승으로 가족이 더는 살 수 없게 된 도시. 집에서 쫓겨날 위기에 처한 한 여성이 2만 5천 달러를 구하기 위해 밤새 사투를 벌인다. 시간이 갈수록 상황은 점점 더 위태로워진다."},"name":"한국어/조선말","iso_639_1":"ko","iso_3166_1":"KR","english_name":"Korean"},{"data":{"title":"A Noite Sempre Chega","runtime":0,"tagline":"25 mil dólares. Uma noite. Sem outra opção.","homepage":"https://www.netflix.com/br/title/81770158","overview":"Prestes a perder sua casa em uma cidade cada vez mais inacessível, uma mulher passa uma noite inteira atrás de 25 mil dólares para evitar o despejo."},"name":"Português","iso_639_1":"pt","iso_3166_1":"BR","english_name":"Portuguese"},{"data":{"title":"Ніч завжди настає","runtime":0,"tagline":"$$25 000. 1 ніч. Інших варіантів немає.","homepage":"https://www.netflix.com/ua/title/81770158","overview":"Жінка з родиною більше не може дозволити собі жити в рідному місті. За одну ніч вона відчайдушно намагається зібрати 25 000 доларів на перший внесок за будинок."},"name":"Український","iso_639_1":"uk","iso_3166_1":"UA","english_name":"Ukrainian"},{"data":{"title":"Ночь всегда приходит","runtime":108,"tagline":"","homepage":"https://www.netflix.com/ru/title/81770158","overview":"Линнет работает на трёх работах. Она живет в обветшалом доме в Портленде вместе со своим старшим братом Кенни, имеющим особенности развития, и их непредсказуемой матерью Дорин. Линнет пытается выкупить дом, чтобы обеспечить семью постоянным жильём и не допустить изъятие Кенни органами опеки. Их арендодатель Дэвид предлагает выгодную сделку по покупке дома. Однако Линнет необходимо, чтобы мать внесла первоначальный взнос. Дорин не приходит на встречу Линнет с Дэвидом для оформления сделки и появляется лишь спустя пару часов с новой машиной. Не сумев уговорить мать вернуть автомобиль в салон, Линнет пытается найти 25 000 долларов к 9 утра следующего дня — именно до этого срока Дэвид согласился ждать в последний раз."},"name":"Pусский","iso_639_1":"ru","iso_3166_1":"RU","english_name":"Russian"},{"data":{"title":"La noche siempre llega","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"https://www.netflix.com/mx/title/81770158","overview":"Arriesgándolo todo para asegurarse un futuro para ella y su hermano, Lynette emprende una peligrosa odisea, enfrentándose a su oscuro pasado."},"name":"Español","iso_639_1":"es","iso_3166_1":"MX","english_name":"Spanish"},{"data":{"title":"คืนวันอันตราย","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"https://www.netflix.com/th/title/81770158","overview":"เมื่อครอบครัวกำลังจะถูกไล่ที่ ในเมืองที่มีค่าใช้จ่ายเกินจะแบกรับ ผู้หญิงที่จนตรอกพยายามหาเงิน 25,000 ดอลลาร์มาให้ได้ภายในหนึ่งคืน จนถลำสู่เส้นทางที่อันตรายขึ้นทุกที"},"name":"ภาษาไทย","iso_639_1":"th","iso_3166_1":"TH","english_name":"Thai"},{"data":{"title":"Zawsze przychodzi noc","runtime":108,"tagline":"25 000 dolarów. Jedna noc. Nie ma innych opcji.","homepage":"https://www.netflix.com/pl/title/81770158","overview":"Kobieta zagrożona eksmisją w mieście, które stało się za drogie dla jej rodziny, zaczyna desperackie i niebezpieczne całonocne poszukiwania, aby zdobyć 25 000 dolarów."},"name":"Polski","iso_639_1":"pl","iso_3166_1":"PL","english_name":"Polish"},{"data":{"title":"","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"https://www.netflix.com/de/title/81770158","overview":"In einer mittlerweile unerschwinglichen Stadt droht einer Familie der Rauswurf. Die verzweifelte Lynette greift zu allen Mitteln, um in nur einer Nacht 25.000 Dollar aufzutreiben."},"name":"Deutsch","iso_639_1":"de","iso_3166_1":"DE","english_name":"German"},{"data":{"title":"黑夜终至","runtime":108,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"改编自威利·弗劳廷所著同名小说，讲述一个女人为拯救家庭、防止家人被驱逐出家族的房子，冒着一切风险踏上一夜的惊险旅程，在波特兰的犯罪圈里筹集资金，期间她被迫直面自己黑暗的过去，最终获得自由。"},"name":"普通话","iso_639_1":"zh","iso_3166_1":"CN","english_name":"Mandarin"},{"data":{"title":"הלילה תמיד מגיע","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"https://www.netflix.com/il/title/81770158","overview":"אישה העומדת בפני פינוי מביתה, בעיר שמשפחתה כבר לא יכולה להרשות לעצמה לגור בה, נגררת למסע נואש ומסוכן יותר ויותר הנמשך כל הלילה בניסיון לגייס 25,000 דולר."},"name":"עִבְרִית","iso_639_1":"he","iso_3166_1":"IL","english_name":"Hebrew"},{"data":{"title":"Vždycky přijde noc","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"https://www.netflix.com/cz/title/81770158","overview":"Zoufalá žena vyrazí na nebezpečnou jízdu nočním městem, kde si už nemůže dovolit žít, aby sehnala pětadvacet tisíc dolarů. Jinak její rodina přijde o střechu nad hlavou."},"name":"Český","iso_639_1":"cs","iso_3166_1":"CZ","english_name":"Czech"},{"data":{"title":"Gece Elbet Çöker","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"https://www.netflix.com/tr/title/81770158","overview":"Ailesinin artık geçinemediği bir şehirde evden çıkarılmakla yüz yüze gelen bir kadın, çaresizlik içinde bir gecede 25.000 dolar bulmak için giderek daha tehlikeli işlere bulaşır."},"name":"Türkçe","iso_639_1":"tr","iso_3166_1":"TR","english_name":"Turkish"},{"data":{"title":"الليل يأتي دائمًا","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"https://www.netflix.com/ae/title/81770158","overview":"أمام تهديد بالإخلاء في مدينة لم تعد أسرتها قادرة على توفير تكاليف معيشتها، تخوض امرأة بقلب يائس رحلة بحث محمومة تحفّها المخاطر طوال الليل من أجل جمع 25 ألف دولار."},"name":"العربية","iso_639_1":"ar","iso_3166_1":"AE","english_name":"Arabic"},{"data":{"title":"الليل يأتي دائمًا","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"https://www.netflix.com/sa/title/81770158","overview":"أمام تهديد بالإخلاء في مدينة لم تعد أسرتها قادرة على توفير تكاليف معيشتها، تخوض امرأة بقلب يائس رحلة بحث محمومة تحفّها المخاطر طوال الليل من أجل جمع 25 ألف دولار."},"name":"العربية","iso_639_1":"ar","iso_3166_1":"SA","english_name":"Arabic"},{"data":{"title":"黑夜終至","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"https://www.netflix.com/tw/title/81770158","overview":"城市的生活已經負擔不起，女子為了不讓家人從棲身之所遭到驅逐，徹夜努力籌措 25,000 美元，處境卻越來越凶險。"},"name":"普通话","iso_639_1":"zh","iso_3166_1":"TW","english_name":"Mandarin"},{"data":{"title":"黑夜終至","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"https://www.netflix.com/hk/title/81770158","overview":"城市的生活已經負擔不起，女子為了不讓家人從棲身之所遭到驅逐，徹夜努力籌措 25,000 美元，處境卻越來越凶險。"},"name":"普通话","iso_639_1":"zh","iso_3166_1":"HK","english_name":"Mandarin"},{"data":{"title":"","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"https://www.netflix.com/dk/title/81770158","overview":"En kvinde er ved at blive sat på gaden i en by, som hendes familie ikke længere har råd til at bo i, og tager på en desperat og farlig natlig jagt efter 25.000 dollars."},"name":"Dansk","iso_639_1":"da","iso_3166_1":"DK","english_name":"Danish"},{"data":{"title":"Noć uvijek dolazi","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"https://www.netflix.com/hr/title/81770158","overview":"Žena koja se nađe pred deložacijom u gradu u kojem njezina obitelj više ne može priuštiti dom krene u očajničku i sve opasniju cjelonoćnu potragu za 25 000 dolara."},"name":"Hrvatski","iso_639_1":"hr","iso_3166_1":"HR","english_name":"Croatian"},{"data":{"title":"黑夜终至","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"https://www.netflix.com/sg-zh/title/81770158","overview":"因为无法继续负担这个城市的生活，一名女子及其家人面临被逐出家园的境况。走投无路的她于是铤而走险，踏入筹集 25000 美元的不眠之夜。"},"name":"普通话","iso_639_1":"zh","iso_3166_1":"SG","english_name":"Mandarin"},{"data":{"title":"","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"https://www.netflix.com/fi/title/81770158","overview":"Häätö uhkaa kaupungissa, jossa perheellä ei ole enää varaa asua. Nainen ryhtyy yhä epätoivoisempiin ja vaarallisempiin tekoihin kasatakseen 25 000 dollaria yhdessä yössä."},"name":"suomi","iso_639_1":"fi","iso_3166_1":"FI","english_name":"Finnish"},{"data":{"title":"","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"https://www.netflix.com/in-hi/title/81770158","overview":"एक महिला का परिवार इतनी तंगी के हालात से गुज़र रहा है कि उन्हें शहर छोड़ना होगा. हताशा में डूबी वह महिला, खतरे मोल लेकर, एक रात में 25,000 डॉलर जुटाने की जद्दोजहद में लग जाती है."},"name":"हिन्दी","iso_639_1":"hi","iso_3166_1":"IN","english_name":"Hindi"},{"data":{"title":"Πάντα Έρχεται η Νύχτα","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"https://www.netflix.com/gr/title/81770158","overview":"Αντιμέτωπη με την έξωση σε μια ακριβή πλέον πόλη, μια γυναίκα βυθίζεται σε μια απελπισμένη και όλο και πιο επικίνδυνη ολονύχτια αναζήτηση για 25.000 δολάρια."},"name":"ελληνικά","iso_639_1":"el","iso_3166_1":"GR","english_name":"Greek"},{"data":{"title":"","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"https://www.netflix.com/nl/title/81770158","overview":"Een vrouw stort zich in een nachtelijke, steeds extremere zoektocht om aan 25.000 dollar te komen, anders wordt ze uit haar huis gezet in een te dure stad."},"name":"Nederlands","iso_639_1":"nl","iso_3166_1":"NL","english_name":"Dutch"},{"data":{"title":"La nuit finit toujours par tomber","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"https://www.netflix.com/ca-fr/title/81770158","overview":"Menacée d'expulsion dans une ville qui n'est plus à la portée de sa famille, une femme plonge dans une quête désespérée et de plus en plus dangereuse pour trouver 25 000 $."},"name":"Français","iso_639_1":"fr","iso_3166_1":"CA","english_name":"French"},{"data":{"title":"","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"https://www.netflix.com/my/title/81770158","overview":"Seorang wanita yang tidak mampu membiayai kehidupan di kota mungkin diusir bersama keluarganya. Dia memulakan pencarian sepanjang malam yang kian berbahaya demi $25,000."},"name":"Bahasa melayu","iso_639_1":"ms","iso_3166_1":"MY","english_name":"Malay"},{"data":{"title":"それでも夜は訪れる","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"https://www.netflix.com/jp/title/81770158","overview":"生活費が高騰した都市で、家族と共に暮らす家から強制退去を迫られる女性。一晩で2万5000ドルをかき集めなければならなくなり、絶望的な状況のなか、危険に飛び込んでいく。"},"name":"日本語","iso_639_1":"ja","iso_3166_1":"JP","english_name":"Japanese"},{"data":{"title":"Mindig eljön az éj","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"https://www.netflix.com/hu/title/81770158","overview":"Egy - a testvérével és anyukájával élő fiatal nő - élete meglehetősen zűrös: teljesen el van adósodva, korábban prostituált is volt, ám jó útra tért, viszont súlyos anyagi gondokkal küzd. Házukat elveszik, ha 24 órán belül nem szerez 25 ezer dollárt. Down-kóros öccsének felügyelete is a tét, úgyhogy a nő mindent megpróbál a pénz előteremtésére. A film voltaképp egyetlen őrült éjszaka története: kocsit lop, aztán egy ismerőse széfjét próbálja feltörni, kokaint árul, mindent megtesz, amit tud. A film szembesíti a nézőt azzal, hogy mennyi mindenre vagyunk képesek azért, hogy elérjük a célunkat, miközben teljesen kiszolgáltatottakká is válhatunk."},"name":"Magyar","iso_639_1":"hu","iso_3166_1":"HU","english_name":"Hungarian"},{"data":{"title":"","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"https://www.netflix.com/id/title/81770158","overview":"Menghadapi pengusiran di kota yang terlalu mahal bagi keluarganya, seorang wanita nekat menempuh cara-cara yang makin berbahaya semalaman demi mendapatkan $25.000."},"name":"Bahasa indonesia","iso_639_1":"id","iso_3166_1":"ID","english_name":"Indonesian"},{"data":{"title":"Mörkret som faller","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"https://www.netflix.com/se/title/81770158","overview":"När en kvinna hotas med vräkning i hemstaden där hon inte längre har råd att bo beger hon sig ut på en desperat och farlig irrfärd genom natten i jakt på 25 000 dollar."},"name":"svenska","iso_639_1":"sv","iso_3166_1":"SE","english_name":"Swedish"},{"data":{"title":"A Noite Sempre Chega","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"https://www.netflix.com/pt/title/81770158","overview":"A enfrentar um despejo numa cidade que se tornou demasiado cara para a sua família, uma mulher parte numa busca frenética e perigosa para obter 25 mil dólares numa noite."},"name":"Português","iso_639_1":"pt","iso_3166_1":"PT","english_name":"Portuguese"},{"data":{"title":"La noche siempre llega","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"https://www.netflix.com/es/title/81770158","overview":"Arriesgándolo todo para asegurarse un futuro para ella y su hermano, Lynette emprende una peligrosa odisea, enfrentándose a su oscuro pasado."},"name":"Español","iso_639_1":"es","iso_3166_1":"ES","english_name":"Spanish"},{"data":{"title":"Noaptea vine mereu","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"https://www.netflix.com/ro/title/81770158","overview":"Riscând evacuarea din orașul în care nu-și mai permite să trăiască, o femeie recurge la măsuri disperate într-o singură noapte, ca să strângă 25.000 de dolari."},"name":"Română","iso_639_1":"ro","iso_3166_1":"RO","english_name":"Romanian"},{"data":{"title":"","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"https://www.netflix.com/no/title/81770158","overview":"En kvinne står i fare for å bli kastet ut av huset sitt i en by familien hennes ikke lenger har råd til å bo i, og en desperat jakt på 25 000 dollar begynner."},"name":"Norsk","iso_639_1":"no","iso_3166_1":"NO","english_name":"Norwegian"},{"data":{"title":"","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"https://www.netflix.com/ph/title/81770158","overview":"Habang nanganganib na mawalan ng matitirhan, napasubo ang isang babae sa isang desperado at delikadong magdamagang paghahanap para makakalap ng $25,000."},"name":"","iso_639_1":"tl","iso_3166_1":"PH","english_name":"Tagalog"},{"data":{"title":"Màn đêm luôn tới","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"https://www.netflix.com/vn/title/81770158","overview":"Sắp mất nhà giữa một thành phố mà gia đình không còn đủ tiền để lưu lại, suốt đêm cô gái nọ tuyệt vọng xoay xở và ngày càng lún sâu vào nguy hiểm hòng kiếm đủ 25.000 đô la."},"name":"Tiếng Việt","iso_639_1":"vi","iso_3166_1":"VN","english_name":"Vietnamese"},{"data":{"title":"Noč vedno pride","runtime":0,"tagline":"25.000 $. 1 noč. Ni drugih opcij.","homepage":"","overview":"Lynette se znajde v brezizhodnem položaju, ko ji grozi deložacija iz doma, v katerem živi z materjo in bratom s posebnimi potrebami. V eni sami, dolgi in nevarni noči mora zbrati 25.000 dolarjev, da bi rešila njihov dom. Njena pot jo vodi skozi niz tveganih srečanj in jo prisili, da se sooči z ljudmi in odločitvami iz svoje preteklosti."},"name":"Slovenščina","iso_639_1":"sl","iso_3166_1":"SI","english_name":"Slovenian"},{"data":{"title":"شب همیشه می‌آید","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":""},"name":"فارسی","iso_639_1":"fa","iso_3166_1":"IR","english_name":"Persian"},{"data":{"title":"Нощта винаги идва","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Изправена пред принудително изгонване от град, в който семейството ѝ вече не може да си позволи да живее, една жена се впуска в отчаяно и все по-опасно нощно търсене на начин да събере 25 000 долара."},"name":"български език","iso_639_1":"bg","iso_3166_1":"BG","english_name":"Bulgarian"},{"data":{"title":"ყოველთვის ღამდება","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":""},"name":"ქართული","iso_639_1":"ka","iso_3166_1":"GE","english_name":"Georgian"},{"data":{"title":"Naktis visada ateina","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Rizikuodama viskuo, kad užtikrintų ateitį sau ir savo broliui, pagrindinė veikėja leidžiasi į pavojingą kelionę, per vieną įtemptą naktį susidurdama su savo tamsia praeitimi. Ši istorija alsuoja įtampa, kai kiekvienas sprendimas gali nulemti visą likimą, o vidinės kovos persipina su išoriniais pavojais. Tai pasakojimas apie išgyvenimą, ryžtą ir pasiaukojimą, kuris nepaliks abejingų."},"name":"Lietuvių","iso_639_1":"lt","iso_3166_1":"LT","english_name":"Lithuanian"}],"reviews_tmdb":[{"id":"68a1d51974174b14ef744e13","url":"https://www.themoviedb.org/review/68a1d51974174b14ef744e13","author":"Manuel São Bento","content":"FULL SPOILER-FREE REVIEW @ https://movieswetextedabout.com/night-always-comes-review-vanessa-kirby-shines-in-a-film-that-fumbles-its-potential/\r\n\r\n\"Night Always Comes falls short of its ambition. There's a powerful story here - the moral erosion provoked by systems that always fail the same people - but the film never finds the most impactful way to tell it.\r\n\r\nAtmosphere and performances elevate the material, with Vanessa Kirby in particular carrying the story's weight with a commitment that deserved a sharper script. Yet between redundancy, lack of subtlety, and indecision between bitter satire and taut thriller, the experience slips into frustration and overemphasis.\r\n\r\nWhen the night ends, what remains is the sense that all that noise amounted to very little meaning.\"\r\n\r\nRating: C-","created_at":"2025-08-17T13:11:53.619Z","updated_at":"2025-08-17T13:11:53.703Z","author_details":{"name":"Manuel São Bento","rating":4,"username":"msbreviews","avatar_path":null}},{"id":"68b00253ca2c3d727fa8a8e9","url":"https://www.themoviedb.org/review/68b00253ca2c3d727fa8a8e9","author":"Horseface","content":"$11","created_at":"2025-08-28T07:16:35.896Z","updated_at":"2025-08-28T07:28:46.910Z","author_details":{"name":"","rating":1,"username":"Horseface","avatar_path":"/zDc2il1Js8wfo2PeV9hUI8eiPbk.png"}},{"id":"68be1cabf23d3e3203947a14","url":"https://www.themoviedb.org/review/68be1cabf23d3e3203947a14","author":"r96sk","content":"<em>'Night Always Comes'</em> delivered a good flick. I do tend to like these gritty crime dramas, so I'm pleased to say that I can list this one in that bracket. Vanessa Kirby comes in with a strong performance, I'm happy to belatedly see her act as the front and centre of a film.\r\n\r\nThere is plenty of action across the 108mins, atmospherically the movie is spot on. It can get quite frustrating but seemingly by design, Doreen is particuarly infuriating - gaslighter of the century, that one! Bar Kirby, this also minimally has Randall Park, Julia Fox, Michael Kelly and Eli Roth.\r\n\r\nI will say some of the dialogue didn't quite do it for me, mainly for Kirby in fact. It just felt unnatural/ill-fitting to me here and there, but in fairness Kirby's acting prowess and the dramatic events are sturdy enough that I quickly forgot any issues I had with that. Worth noting, still.","created_at":"2025-09-08T00:00:43.448Z","updated_at":"2025-09-08T00:00:43.541Z","author_details":{"name":"","rating":8,"username":"r96sk","avatar_path":"/mwR7rFHoDcobAx1i61I3skzMW3U.jpg"}},{"id":"693b0b3ff0fed80e8e012d84","url":"https://www.themoviedb.org/review/693b0b3ff0fed80e8e012d84","author":".titanium.","content":"Added to the list of movies I wish I never watched. Not entertaining and writing was horrible. Sometimes I wonder how these types of movies even get made, but do not recommend watching this movie unless you are a family member of someone unfortunate to be casted in it.","created_at":"2025-12-11T18:19:43.442Z","updated_at":"2025-12-11T20:09:26.659Z","author_details":{"name":"","rating":4,"username":".titanium.","avatar_path":null}}],"recommendations":[{"id":1139695,"adult":false,"title":"She's Got No Name","video":false,"overview":"A bizarre case caused thousands of waves. There are different opinions on the truth. When the whole story of the case was gradually restored like pieces of a puzzle, people realized that the truth was not that important anymore.","genre_ids":[18,80],"media_type":"movie","popularity":1.1245,"vote_count":9,"poster_path":"/2C1yy7lPYAYvbtW8bDckGGdPhmt.jpg","release_date":"2025-06-14","vote_average":4.7,"backdrop_path":"/busvJ951z67XMmGbAWgFHhXwdSf.jpg","original_title":"酱园弄·悬案","original_language":"zh"},{"id":1214052,"adult":false,"title":"To a Land Unknown","video":false,"overview":"Cousins Chatila and Reda are saving to pay for fake passports to get out of Athens. When Reda loses their hard-earned cash to his drug addiction, Chatila hatches an extreme plan to pose as smugglers in an attempt to get them out of their desperate situation before it is too late.","genre_ids":[53,80],"media_type":"movie","popularity":0.4697,"vote_count":9,"poster_path":"/wjr6q8kw1HkkpoeodvUOjQXFlom.jpg","release_date":"2025-02-14","vote_average":7.1,"backdrop_path":"/49CjA88b278yvTswsJs1jUJTAbx.jpg","original_title":"Σε μια άγνωστη χώρα","original_language":"el"},{"id":1428210,"adult":false,"title":"One Hit Wonder","video":false,"overview":"When big dreams meet second chances, two dreamers Entoy and Lorina chase fame in the world of '90s OPM. Will they make it?","genre_ids":[10749,10402,18],"media_type":"movie","popularity":0.306,"vote_count":9,"poster_path":"/kdHEtyOoB8cyFDwqFMMGK1q0RlM.jpg","release_date":"2025-08-21","vote_average":6.4,"backdrop_path":"/99yYnWssK8v67jbin9vosSysnhT.jpg","original_title":"One Hit Wonder","original_language":"tl"},{"id":336806,"adult":false,"title":"The Here After","video":false,"overview":"When John returns home to his father after serving time in prison, he is looking forward to starting his life afresh. However, in the local community his crime is neither forgotten nor forgiven.","genre_ids":[18],"media_type":"movie","popularity":0.2366,"vote_count":44,"poster_path":"/taRuclzevcoTBNlT72rlfdILxsd.jpg","release_date":"2015-01-20","vote_average":6.3,"backdrop_path":"/2KBm2Q6NzwdtOH5Gav9WgkdHlpw.jpg","original_title":"Efterskalv","original_language":"sv"},{"id":43474,"adult":false,"title":"Io tigro, tu tigri, egli tigra","video":false,"overview":"Three short stories full of absurd Italian humor. Episode 1: Oddjobs man Elia is hired to be a waiter and soon finds himself caught up in a plot to knock off his mistress (in more ways than one). Episode 2: Della is convinced that aliens are on their way to consume the world and before long ends up a guinea pig on a spaceship from the planet Phobos. Episode 3: Roberto becomes a Bersaglieri in the Italian army and nearly causes a war between Italy and Switzerland over a packet of cigarettes.","genre_ids":[35],"media_type":"movie","popularity":0.1936,"vote_count":35,"poster_path":"/vq8jg3Ghdz6LgvOIePqPt2m4pbc.jpg","release_date":"1978-09-21","vote_average":4.886,"backdrop_path":"/aKGmMJ77IoykJpr2txEXADQg1ul.jpg","original_title":"Io tigro, tu tigri, egli tigra","original_language":"it"},{"id":56830,"adult":false,"title":"Johns","video":false,"overview":"It's the day before Christmas, the day before John's 21st birthday. He's a prostitute on Santa Monica Blvd in L.A., and he wants to spend that night and the next day at the posh Park Plaza Hotel. Meanwhile, Donner, a lad new to the streets, wants John to leave the city with him. John spends the day trying to figure out how to deal with Donner's friendship.","genre_ids":[18,10749],"media_type":"movie","popularity":0.6132,"vote_count":24,"poster_path":"/dIiAsjLNB0ud1MiwXxv1GEuuuXS.jpg","release_date":"1996-12-10","vote_average":5.2,"backdrop_path":"/mir57K4jzuIzBXSne6Wo8lLwrZg.jpg","original_title":"Johns","original_language":"en"},{"id":600014,"adult":false,"title":"Iron Fists and Kung Fu Kicks","video":false,"overview":"The fantastic story of how an ancient martial art, Chinese kung fu, conquered the world through the hundreds of films that were produced in Hong Kong over the decades, transformed Western action cinema and inspired the birth of cultural movements such as blaxploitation, hip hop music, parkour and Wakaliwood cinema.","genre_ids":[99,36],"media_type":"movie","popularity":1.0342,"vote_count":58,"poster_path":"/1t0SsQqmfYVuD3MBCIB4muGllAP.jpg","release_date":"2019-08-14","vote_average":6.7,"backdrop_path":"/wtHejZOVkAZtZ8L8o1g3KNE56xJ.jpg","original_title":"Iron Fists and Kung Fu Kicks","original_language":"en"},{"id":1366200,"adult":false,"title":"The Girl Who Wasn't Dead","video":false,"overview":"Erica vanishes, believed a victim of a serial killer, but emerges at her murder trial 3 years later, having run away to live secretly with her older boyfriend near her mother's home, banned from seeing him.","genre_ids":[18,80,10770],"media_type":"movie","popularity":0.4115,"vote_count":10,"poster_path":"/2jtvp9SXqfAlIooogAJf0P03hoq.jpg","release_date":"2024-10-05","vote_average":5.4,"backdrop_path":"/6qLeKnYFL5vv3kS8hajvti1tiua.jpg","original_title":"The Girl Who Wasn't Dead","original_language":"en"},{"id":355772,"adult":false,"title":"ToY","video":false,"overview":"ToY is a drama about two lost souls from disparate backgrounds who find each other amid the desperation and glamour of Los Angeles, forging an unlikely relationship that spirals into tragic chaos.","genre_ids":[10749,53],"media_type":"movie","popularity":0.7444,"vote_count":18,"poster_path":"/38hm7meoMAGlRK0H8CrbzNCz4J9.jpg","release_date":"2015-08-22","vote_average":5.278,"backdrop_path":"/6hFiJoXLX4uLh18BjXvU5qUH3tR.jpg","original_title":"ToY","original_language":"en"},{"id":59481,"adult":false,"title":"A House in the Hills","video":false,"overview":"An aspiring actress gets a housesitting job and finds herself in a cat-and-mouse game with a deadly ex-con.","genre_ids":[53,10749],"media_type":"movie","popularity":0.3233,"vote_count":20,"poster_path":"/7rXD3TzhWNSjrQH3DgpYcg0V3bU.jpg","release_date":"1993-01-20","vote_average":5.7,"backdrop_path":"/83hByEoe4uDhQpAU3jOcrcROTbV.jpg","original_title":"A House in the Hills","original_language":"en"},{"id":1297454,"adult":false,"title":"The Death That Awaits","video":false,"overview":"A drifter searching for answers to a mystery from her past takes on a job looking after a sick teen who is undergoing a mysterious transformation her family will do anything to stop.","genre_ids":[27,53],"media_type":"movie","popularity":0.3023,"vote_count":10,"poster_path":"/7hloUkIXB1Jc0xjSFlO4dcVfzdt.jpg","release_date":"2025-02-06","vote_average":5.35,"backdrop_path":"/impZCV9HiZ3bIrKK5bD1TKRsfVM.jpg","original_title":"The Death That Awaits","original_language":"en"},{"id":785521,"adult":false,"title":"Battle: Freestyle","video":false,"overview":"Amalie and Mikael lead their street dance team to the finals in France but tough competition and personal distractions threaten to ruin their dreams.","genre_ids":[10749,18],"media_type":"movie","popularity":0.4251,"vote_count":68,"poster_path":"/6D6QumiHEhnpZG12Ibjy2BxA6n4.jpg","release_date":"2022-04-01","vote_average":5.5,"backdrop_path":"/8WpRRiz3qQqzBiifCTm1dW0b6bs.jpg","original_title":"Battle: Freestyle","original_language":"no"},{"id":1437237,"adult":false,"title":"Performance: A Dangerous Game","video":false,"overview":"Giada and Carlo have been a couple for many years, both artists. He is a writer looking for a new story to tell, she is a dancer struggling as she directs her first experimental dance show. When Peter Drago comes into their lives, neither can imagine how much everything is about to change. Carlo is fascinated by him, finding in him a new creative inspiration, while Giada is increasingly restless, fearing that her past may come back to surface. But the truth always finds a way to emerge.","genre_ids":[53,18],"media_type":"movie","popularity":0.3621,"vote_count":28,"poster_path":"/xQbyabXxKAS44yXb5BcNmInre5e.jpg","release_date":"2025-03-13","vote_average":4.911,"backdrop_path":"/qBwaMyVGjscDP1r0uAYkg88DDG6.jpg","original_title":"Gioco pericoloso","original_language":"it"},{"id":43100,"adult":false,"title":"General Della Rovere","video":false,"overview":"The Gestapo forces con man Victorio Bardone to impersonate a dead partisan general in order to extract information from his fellow inmates.","genre_ids":[18,10752],"media_type":"movie","popularity":0.4494,"vote_count":143,"poster_path":"/dTynqWaUm92ecwxCuMkTdHCoOfx.jpg","release_date":"1959-10-07","vote_average":7.448,"backdrop_path":"/uRMjUzSuVfbzuZkenEV9DkHxOR.jpg","original_title":"Il generale Della Rovere","original_language":"it"},{"id":1280089,"adult":false,"title":"The Siege at Thorn High","video":false,"overview":"Edwin promised to his sister on her deathbed to find her son she gave up a long time ago. Edwin's quest brought him to become a substitute teacher in Duri High School, Jakarta, a school for juvenile delinquents. There he must face the most violent students to find his nephew. When he eventually finds the boy, a city-wide riot erupts and Edwin is trapped in the school with the cruel kids out for his blood.","genre_ids":[28,80,53],"media_type":"movie","popularity":1.3213,"vote_count":37,"poster_path":"/uis9PJkI6WHRczCumsfPFaaUAxm.jpg","release_date":"2025-04-17","vote_average":7.4,"backdrop_path":"/dcpXPUVEqiuYclsnael3bJjos4B.jpg","original_title":"Pengepungan di Bukit Duri","original_language":"id"},{"id":1310871,"adult":false,"title":"The Cavern Crimes","video":false,"overview":"An intense suspense thriller with an attractive blend of crime and mystery set in the unique historical backdrop of the Atapuerca paleontological site, home of the oldest human remains outside of Africa.","genre_ids":[80,9648,53],"media_type":"movie","popularity":1.3638,"vote_count":39,"poster_path":"/o410zKXtZYy2vVBcQJPxzOc9KYc.jpg","release_date":"2025-04-04","vote_average":5.692,"backdrop_path":"/wnVxIPc14Af9ztf1h3YzelZuw6W.jpg","original_title":"La huella del mal","original_language":"es"},{"id":537921,"adult":false,"title":"Fixed","video":false,"overview":"After learning he's getting neutered, a dog has 24 hours to squeeze in one last balls-to-the-wall adventure with the boys.","genre_ids":[16,35],"media_type":"movie","popularity":2.6474,"vote_count":137,"poster_path":"/udtlwWSJ45S0uQm29BvFvjPJGW0.jpg","release_date":"2025-08-13","vote_average":6.237,"backdrop_path":"/vmWgToiWzgWxzGtdbeQFrtuS2BN.jpg","original_title":"Fixed","original_language":"en"},{"id":936108,"adult":false,"title":"Smurfs","video":false,"overview":"When Papa Smurf is mysteriously taken by evil wizards, Razamel and Gargamel, Smurfette leads the Smurfs on a mission into the real world to save him. With the help of new friends, the Smurfs must discover what defines their destiny to save the universe.","genre_ids":[16,10751,14],"media_type":"movie","popularity":8.769,"vote_count":240,"poster_path":"/8o6lkhL32xQJeB52IIG1us5BVey.jpg","release_date":"2025-07-05","vote_average":5.89,"backdrop_path":"/9whEVuKte4Qi0LI4TzPf7glinJW.jpg","original_title":"Smurfs","original_language":"en"},{"id":1208983,"adult":false,"title":"Neighborhood Watch","video":false,"overview":"When a mentally ill young man thinks he witnesses an abduction and the police refuse to believe him, he reluctantly turns to his next door neighbor – a bitter, retired security guard – to help him find the missing woman.","genre_ids":[53,80],"media_type":"movie","popularity":4.852,"vote_count":106,"poster_path":"/n1KcNdCrz5s3ruij9eiT5IARter.jpg","release_date":"2025-04-25","vote_average":6.4,"backdrop_path":"/n8uHu75o4wIBIBN3fG9qISXgqU0.jpg","original_title":"Neighborhood Watch","original_language":"en"},{"id":1285406,"adult":false,"title":"Enemigos","video":false,"overview":"Chimo turns 18 years and comes from a humble and supportive family. Since childhood he was bullied and even today, while working multiple jobs and dreaming of starting his own business, he continues to face his bully: El Rubio. When Chimo has the opportunity for revenge, he never imagines what begins as an act of retaliation could turn into an unexpected friendship that'll change both their lives.","genre_ids":[18],"media_type":"movie","popularity":1.0264,"vote_count":63,"poster_path":"/931RWObebU1Y4EUS2fpwmZQRGPs.jpg","release_date":"2025-05-09","vote_average":7.746,"backdrop_path":"/fem2Q5hHroXEYsGWHOC7VMpj1cK.jpg","original_title":"Enemigos","original_language":"es"}],"similar_content":[{"id":869602,"adult":false,"title":"Lead Me Home","video":false,"overview":"Poignant stories of homelessness on the West Coast of the US frame this cinematic portrait of a surging humanitarian crisis.","genre_ids":[99,18],"popularity":0.5906,"vote_count":127,"poster_path":"/rrsrOldUfXn5vd5HP3BAYxLTjpO.jpg","release_date":"2021-09-03","vote_average":6.35,"backdrop_path":"/tJyvDf1lj4uKySKlyMjyoaoOwyB.jpg","original_title":"Lead Me Home","original_language":"en"},{"id":12611,"adult":false,"title":"The Fury","video":false,"overview":"When a devious plot separates CIA agent Peter Sandza from his son, Robin, the distraught father manages to see through the ruse. Taken because of his psychic abilities, Robin is being held by Ben Childress, who is studying people with supernatural powers in hopes of developing their talents as weapons. Soon Peter pairs up with Gillian, a teen who has telekinesis, to find and rescue Robin.","genre_ids":[27,878,53],"popularity":1.3255,"vote_count":392,"poster_path":"/tkIXykrfndqf11Lb7U5RbIRa13b.jpg","release_date":"1978-03-10","vote_average":6.297,"backdrop_path":"/bgTgA6ZckxKMy0oQyEFenxmxdGK.jpg","original_title":"The Fury","original_language":"en"},{"id":283235,"adult":false,"title":"99 Homes","video":false,"overview":"After his family is evicted from their home, proud and desperate construction worker Dennis Nash tries to win his home back by striking a deal with the devil and working for Rick Carver, the corrupt real estate broker who evicted him.","genre_ids":[18],"popularity":4.4848,"vote_count":815,"poster_path":"/6Zul5Spndok1WriSMfiyQFbAyLY.jpg","release_date":"2015-09-25","vote_average":6.799,"backdrop_path":"/icCQi9Tnyx86C987IoIFchxqMof.jpg","original_title":"99 Homes","original_language":"en"},{"id":13964,"adult":false,"title":"The Machine Girl","video":false,"overview":"The life of a young, Japanese schoolgirl is destroyed when her family is killed by a Ninja-Yakuza family. Her hand cut off, she replaces it with various machines-of-death, and seeks revenge.","genre_ids":[28,12,35,80,27,53],"popularity":0.9363,"vote_count":222,"poster_path":"/qccgrtiVYzEBPIvWz7hEY5a2Aax.jpg","release_date":"2008-01-02","vote_average":5.998,"backdrop_path":"/iHwZL5pehrFhSISA9pXFErrLuNf.jpg","original_title":"片腕マシンガール","original_language":"ja"},{"id":283601,"adult":false,"title":"Galveston","video":false,"overview":"After a violent encounter, Roy finds Rocky and sees something in her eyes that prompts a fateful decision. He takes her with him as he flees to Galveston, an action as ill-advised as it is inescapable.","genre_ids":[53],"popularity":1.3312,"vote_count":535,"poster_path":"/u3hDPc70JEWbrLruk6sni1OcODe.jpg","release_date":"2018-10-10","vote_average":6.117,"backdrop_path":"/sX8QB6p9nTltEnKLiFE2lXad7cc.jpg","original_title":"Galveston","original_language":"en"},{"id":13685,"adult":false,"title":"Bottle Rocket","video":false,"overview":"Upon his release from a mental hospital following a nervous breakdown, the directionless Anthony joins his friend Dignan, who seems far less sane than the former. Dignan has hatched a harebrained scheme for an as-yet-unspecified crime spree that somehow involves his former boss, the (supposedly) legendary Mr. Henry.","genre_ids":[35,80,18],"popularity":1.8628,"vote_count":1156,"poster_path":"/wOPiNYt9V3Cbr9Izeddwj7nU8RT.jpg","release_date":"1996-02-21","vote_average":6.7,"backdrop_path":"/wWZjmgJC2m2jy4UAPtRAsakNtG7.jpg","original_title":"Bottle Rocket","original_language":"en"},{"id":13552,"adult":false,"title":"The Doom Generation","video":false,"overview":"Jordan White and Amy Blue, two troubled teens, pick up an adolescent drifter, Xavier Red. Together, the threesome embarks on a sex- and violence-filled journey through a United States of psychos and quickie marts.","genre_ids":[35,80,18],"popularity":1.1779,"vote_count":302,"poster_path":"/cRzRj2UBvIH8ryWhu5PNL2PzV7j.jpg","release_date":"1995-10-20","vote_average":6.5,"backdrop_path":"/9mHvO0PzmEgxDtmRq3VeTVELYqb.jpg","original_title":"The Doom Generation","original_language":"en"},{"id":1462908,"adult":false,"title":"Hermes Trismegisto","video":false,"overview":"A foreigner searchs for Hermes Trismegisto in order to become its pupil.","genre_ids":[35,53],"popularity":0.185,"vote_count":1,"poster_path":"/7pscagySSYGJWuo0Iw3YQo9DE1H.jpg","release_date":"2025-04-05","vote_average":10,"backdrop_path":null,"original_title":"Hermes Trismegisto","original_language":"pt"},{"id":1072876,"adult":false,"title":"Self Reliance","video":false,"overview":"When a man is offered a million dollars to play a game in which hunters try to kill him, he thinks he has found the perfect loophole: they can only attack when he’s alone. His only problem is that none of his friends or family believe the game is real. Forced to seek companionship in unexpected places, he navigates the bizarre challenge with humor, paranoia, and a surprising search for connection.","genre_ids":[35,53],"popularity":2.8476,"vote_count":290,"poster_path":"/hlSWmmuuLeV1p3YcIkU59khEHLY.jpg","release_date":"2024-01-03","vote_average":5.922,"backdrop_path":"/jsp420JTZ7EK5LhpwzunE1Pu43d.jpg","original_title":"Self Reliance","original_language":"en"},{"id":15765,"adult":false,"title":"What's Love Got to Do with It","video":false,"overview":"Singer Tina Turner rises to stardom while mustering the courage to break free from her abusive husband Ike.","genre_ids":[18,10402,36],"popularity":1.2619,"vote_count":351,"poster_path":"/btC4819GhihmkCELqO3qgepNGos.jpg","release_date":"1993-06-09","vote_average":7,"backdrop_path":"/ow5u27LapD6xMe24o2ITnZDoz7z.jpg","original_title":"What's Love Got to Do with It","original_language":"en"},{"id":15767,"adult":false,"title":"Godzilla: Final Wars","video":false,"overview":"Humanity finally rids themselves of Godzilla, imprisoning him in an icy tomb in the South Pole. All is peaceful until various monsters emerge to lay waste to Earth's cities. Overwhelmed, humanity is seemingly saved by a race of benevolent aliens known as Xiliens. But not all is what it seems with these bizarre visitors. If humanity wishes to survive, they must reluctantly resurrect their most hated enemy, Godzilla.","genre_ids":[28,12,878,14,53],"popularity":2.3103,"vote_count":351,"poster_path":"/21lWA4YyYppVnwAPOiBkGrt2FGr.jpg","release_date":"2004-12-04","vote_average":7.058,"backdrop_path":"/irLLP6uZRB10P4bCGZMzlGB5p6c.jpg","original_title":"ゴジラ ファイナルウォーズ","original_language":"ja"},{"id":467909,"adult":false,"title":"In the Heights","video":false,"overview":"The story of Usnavi, a bodega owner who has mixed feelings about closing his store and retiring to the Dominican Republic or staying in Washington Heights.","genre_ids":[18,10749],"popularity":1.5347,"vote_count":773,"poster_path":"/RO4KoJyoQMQzh9z76d4v4FJMmJ.jpg","release_date":"2021-06-10","vote_average":7.1,"backdrop_path":"/uEJuqp08dH6IQwZJGASlPZOXqKu.jpg","original_title":"In the Heights","original_language":"en"},{"id":467938,"adult":false,"title":"Revenge","video":false,"overview":"Jen's romantic getaway with her wealthy married boyfriend is disrupted when his friends arrive for an impromptu hunting trip. Tension mounts at the house until the situation culminates in an unexpected way.","genre_ids":[28,27,53],"popularity":4.0647,"vote_count":2030,"poster_path":"/AbWKFxt459cWYTNPTcbpB0i2hQp.jpg","release_date":"2018-02-07","vote_average":6.505,"backdrop_path":"/31HKH7MpovHT4bTvMpnwbWl1d1G.jpg","original_title":"Revenge","original_language":"fr"},{"id":4550,"adult":false,"title":"Lady Vengeance","video":false,"overview":"Released after being wrongfully convicted and imprisoned for 13 years, a woman begins executing her elaborate plan of retribution.","genre_ids":[18,53],"popularity":3.7502,"vote_count":1870,"poster_path":"/3Oy3iLMqD79us2iAUD6fKqWebYU.jpg","release_date":"2005-07-29","vote_average":7.522,"backdrop_path":"/wP1nu98mgiSOyuPmMWdZ8109S9j.jpg","original_title":"친절한 금자씨","original_language":"ko"},{"id":4723,"adult":false,"title":"Southland Tales","video":false,"overview":"Set in the futuristic landscape of Los Angeles on July 4, 2008, as it stands on the brink of social, economic and environmental disaster. Boxer Santaros is an action star who's stricken with amnesia. His life intertwines with Krysta Now, an adult film star developing her own reality television project, and Ronald Taverner, a Hermosa Beach police officer who holds the key to a vast conspiracy.","genre_ids":[878,53,35],"popularity":1.8045,"vote_count":591,"poster_path":"/7dbIDQ80z4bxiDlAvxRwc5TI44C.jpg","release_date":"2007-11-14","vote_average":5.217,"backdrop_path":"/oaT5yMG61XetddVmymGrDVeoCg4.jpg","original_title":"Southland Tales","original_language":"en"},{"id":5548,"adult":false,"title":"RoboCop","video":false,"overview":"In a violent, near-apocalyptic Detroit, evil corporation Omni Consumer Products wins a contract from the city government to privatize the police force. To test their crime-eradicating cyborgs, the company leads street cop Alex Murphy into an armed confrontation with crime lord Boddicker so they can use his body to support their untested RoboCop prototype. But when RoboCop learns of the company's nefarious plans, he turns on his masters.","genre_ids":[28,53,878],"popularity":8.9471,"vote_count":5591,"poster_path":"/esmAU0fCO28FbS6bUBKLAzJrohZ.jpg","release_date":"1987-07-17","vote_average":7.352,"backdrop_path":"/pRSTtNlcADoQkfeBGtFQNE1FDpb.jpg","original_title":"RoboCop","original_language":"en"},{"id":657851,"adult":false,"title":"The Heist","video":false,"overview":"Four young men are sitting in a car at a train crossing and waiting for the train to pass.","genre_ids":[18,80],"popularity":2.7943,"vote_count":2,"poster_path":"/2ZHUkl7xvFcTmMOwAe8Ljp8Hxek.jpg","release_date":"2000-01-01","vote_average":5,"backdrop_path":null,"original_title":"Kuppet","original_language":"da"},{"id":1062323,"adult":false,"title":"The Champion","video":false,"overview":"Diego has just been voted best young player in Europe and at the age of 20 he is on his way to making his team, Atlético de Madrid, champions of La Liga. But his impulsive and conflictive character makes the club, fed up with his excesses, hire Álex, a withdrawn and lonely psychology professor, to improve his behaviour. The two will have no choice but to learn to understand each other.","genre_ids":[18,10751,35],"popularity":0.7497,"vote_count":45,"poster_path":"/wBftPyDCfxZ9XD5J5X6LYzFzZYK.jpg","release_date":"2024-07-12","vote_average":5.356,"backdrop_path":"/sRuoaYjWLLngZo2XYKPwyL9SYxY.jpg","original_title":"El campeón","original_language":"es"},{"id":10243,"adult":false,"title":"The Flight of the Phoenix","video":false,"overview":"A cargo aircraft crashes in a sandstorm in the Sahara with less than a dozen men on board. One of the passengers is an airplane designer who comes up with the idea of ripping off the undamaged wing and using it as the basis for a replacement aircraft they need to build before their food and water run out.","genre_ids":[12,18],"popularity":1.6619,"vote_count":358,"poster_path":"/zrzLl7NWdjwGhVE7bqpOAxMVtF.jpg","release_date":"1965-12-15","vote_average":7.214,"backdrop_path":"/61cz8dZkyIo9m5bVwwfrYcvVZiK.jpg","original_title":"The Flight of the Phoenix","original_language":"en"},{"id":10281,"adult":false,"title":"Friday the 13th Part VII: The New Blood","video":false,"overview":"Tina Shepard, a telekinetic teenage girl, accidentally unchains Jason from his watery grave, allowing him to go on another killing spree in the area.","genre_ids":[27,53],"popularity":2.206,"vote_count":1179,"poster_path":"/rUzk9Qnyz2FZGxHMBrq6DYIQZkO.jpg","release_date":"1988-05-13","vote_average":5.482,"backdrop_path":"/roHX6N0VkySKBlramHUw1zdMQHB.jpg","original_title":"Friday the 13th Part VII: The New Blood","original_language":"en"}],"external_ids":{"imdb_id":"tt31567422","twitter_id":null,"facebook_id":null,"wikidata_id":"Q126077186","instagram_id":null,"metacritic_id":"movie/night-always-comes","rotten_tomatoes_id":"m/night_always_comes"},"social_ids":{"twitter":null,"facebook":null,"instagram":null},"gdvg_id":118235,"wiki_plot":"$12","wiki_synopsis":"","wiki_episode_guide":"","wiki_production":"In March 2024, it was announced the film would be produced by Aluna Entertainment under their agreement with Netflix. The film, based on the 2021 novel by Willy Vlautin, would be directed by Benjamin Caron from a script by Sarah Conradt. Vanessa Kirby would star in and also produce the film. Also producing are Lauren Dark, Benjamin and Jodie Caron, Gary Levinsohn, and Billy Hines.\n\nThe cast also includes Jennifer Jason Leigh, Zack Gottsagen, Stephan James, Julia Fox, Eli Roth, Randall Park, and Michael Kelly.\n\nPrincipal photography took place from May 14 to July 2, 2024, in Portland, Oregon, and at Mt. Hood Community College in Gresham, Oregon.","wiki_cast_notes":"","wiki_reception":"","wiki_soundtrack":"","wiki_release":"","wiki_accolades":"","release_dates":[{"iso_3166_1":"AD","release_dates":[{"note":"Netflix","type":4,"iso_639_1":"","descriptors":[],"release_date":"2025-08-15T00:00:00.000Z","certification":""}]},{"iso_3166_1":"AE","release_dates":[{"note":"Netflix","type":4,"is